data.description: Welcome to La Jolla Palms. Come to take a tour of this exciting new home on the market, offering 2 bedrooms downstairs and 4 bedrooms upstairs, sits in a beautiful newer neighborhood, home offers lots of extras, Reverse Osmosis water softener, Interior Speakers throughout home inside and outside, Electric Fireplace, Granite Countertops, Pergola Style Patio, Batting Cage, Ceramic Tile Floors downstairs, 2 A/C units on property, great location. Come see today,
